	<text id="ruskin_to_Joan_july_02_1867_2">
	    
	    <header>
	        <inventNo>2003L01522</inventNo>
	    </header>
	
	    <body>
	        <div type="text">
	            <pb n="1"/>           
	            <opener>
	                <placeName><!-- match letter exactly, delete if unnecessary -->
	                    <rs key="Q31105500" type="place">Huntly Burn</rs>
	                </placeName>
	                <date when="1867-07-02"><!-- match letter exactly, delete if unnecessary -->
	                    <rs type="date">2nd July</rs>
	                </date>
	                <salute>My dearest wee <rs key="76205504" type="person">Amie</rs></salute><!-- match letter exactly, delete if unnecessary -->
	            </opener>
	            
	            <p id="p1">
	                <s id="s1">I had sent the princpial letter I write to you to-day, to <rs key="Q5523474" type="place">
	                    Garlieston</rs> - thinking it likely my letter from <rs key="low_wood" type="place">Low-wood</rs>
	                    might make you delay your journey to <rs key="Q4093" type="place">Glasgow</rs>, but in case you
	                    have been forced to go on the day you intended, this is only to tell you that I go to-morrow to
	                    <rs key="Q1025076" type="place"><hi rend="underline">Keswick</hi></rs><add hand="#JR" place="above"><expan>
	                        Cumb<ex cert="high">ri</ex>a</expan></add>, where a letter to the Postoffice will find me, and tell me what arrangements you would like me to make about a little visit to <rs key="c_agnew" type="person">your mother</rs>.</s>
	            </p>
	            
	            <closer>
	                <salute>Ever your loving Cuzzie</salute><!-- optional - delete if unnecessary -->
	                <signed><!-- optional - delete if unnecessary -->
	                    <rs key="73859585" type="person">J Ruskin</rs>
	                </signed>
	             </closer>
	        </div>
	    </body>
	</text>      
	
